{
  "id": "6285b80a9e028e0023e0e653",
  "title": "一言物申す人",
  "created": 1652930575,
  "updated": 1652931518,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6285b80a9e028e0023e0e653",
      "text": "一言物申す人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930575,
      "updated": 1652930582
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b818aff09e0000a0ce00",
      "text": "「一言物申す」人が嫌われる原理",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930585,
      "updated": 1652930603
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b82baff09e0000a0ce02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930603,
      "updated": 1652930612
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b848aff09e0000a0ce03",
      "text": "　生産的な一言を言うためには先に情報収集が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930632,
      "updated": 1652930657
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b858aff09e0000a0ce04",
      "text": "　情報収集を行わず、たまたま目にしたニュース記事やツイートに対して「一言物申す」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930649,
      "updated": 1652930693
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b885aff09e0000a0ce05",
      "text": "　これに対して「[生産的な議論]をする気がない」という意図の推察が行われる(A)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930693,
      "updated": 1652931457
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b89faff09e0000a0ce06",
      "text": "　「生産的な議論をする気がないのに一言物申すのはなぜか？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930719,
      "updated": 1652930735
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b8aeaff09e0000a0ce07",
      "text": "　「一言物申す」ことによって「物申した自分」になることが気持ち良いからやっているのでは？と推察される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930735,
      "updated": 1652930782
    },
    {
      "id": "6285bb86aff09e0000a0ce19",
      "text": "　　[他人を下げることで自分が高まる妄想]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652931462,
      "updated": 1652931518
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b8deaff09e0000a0ce08",
      "text": "　つまり欲望を充足するための活動だ、と解釈される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930782,
      "updated": 1652930834
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b819aff09e0000a0ce01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930586,
      "updated": 1652930586
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b916aff09e0000a0ce09",
      "text": "議論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930838,
      "updated": 1652930841
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b919aff09e0000a0ce0b",
      "text": "　この(A)の部分は「観測できない他人の[内面の推測]」なので正当性があるとは言えない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930841,
      "updated": 1652931442
    },
    {
      "id": "6285b918aff09e0000a0ce0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652930841,
      "updated": 1652930841
    },
    {
      "id": "6285bba3aff09e0000a0ce1a",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652931491,
      "updated": 1652931492
    },
    {
      "id": "6285bba4aff09e0000a0ce1c",
      "text": "　[批評は凡庸な輩の避難所]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652931493,
      "updated": 1652931494
    },
    {
      "id": "6285bba4aff09e0000a0ce1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1652931492,
      "updated": 1652931492
    }
  ]
}